1.name: Forecast Flow
1.description: Weather App built using React, allowing users to check the current weather conditions for a specific city. It integrates with the OpenWeatherMap API to fetch real-time weather data and displays it in a user-friendly interface.

2.name: Git Searcher
2.description: Create a tool that, given a username, retrieves and presents the repositories and project links associated with that user. This tool offers a streamlined way to access and explore a user's projects and contributions within a single interface.

3.name: Tail Trove
3.description: Tail-Trove is a beginner-friendly e-commerce project built using the MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js) stack. This project aims to provide a foundational understanding of building a basic pet e-commerce website with essential functionalities.
